show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: An 8-year-old boy returns with memories of his past life, driven by a single purpose — to change his father’s destiny. This emotional thriller weaves together love, revenge, and the high-stakes world of the stock market into one gripping narrative
